 *
 * Synthetic fixture: a ModelDesign whose object instance has a
 * TypeDefinition that resolves to an ObjectType declared in a separate
 * NodeSet2 input (CrossModelTypes.NodeSet2.xml). Exercises the
 * ModelDesign -> NodeSet2 cross-model resolution path.
